{
  "stem": "10.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was very crowded, because normally, a barrack is not-- is maybe occupied by 100 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we were 200 and more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They asked me from where I come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I told them from Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were surprised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's already from Poland, in October, '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They're already-- they're bringing already Jews from Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was the first Pole-- not only Jews-- but the first Pole in a German concentration camp in '39, in October.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We ask question, and they answer us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're just waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, we get up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the evening, we go to-- on the straw sacks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We spread out the straw sacks, and we lay down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this is it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no work for us, but they had a new method.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the morning, when we got up, we got this little-- a container with a hot, black water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They called it coffee, but we called it water, because this was not coffee-- and nothing else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we were taken out to the roll-call in the morning, in front of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were standing, next to us, we had to put up the bodies of people who died next to the-- to us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the SS man came, the first thing he asked-- not how many people, but how many dead?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was more interested in the dead people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the block eldest gave him the report, so and so many, he said, oh, only 15?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's not enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tomorrow, I send.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want to see more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were only interested to kill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after he went, we had to sit down in a crouching position this way-- hands behind the neck-- and sit this way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
